                     <interp inst="t18461026-2115-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing 1 pair of trowsers, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 3 shirts, 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 pairs of drawers, <hi rend="italic">is.</hi>; 1 other shirt, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 3 pain of stockings, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 bag, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18461026-name-701" type="victimName">
